If the index that uses this policy fails to reach at least 100 documents, then it will never be deleted due to:

https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/243e863f6e862074b564f909e90a8fd83ae8ad01/x-pack/plugin/core/src/main/java/org/elasticsearch/xpack/core/indexlifecycle/RolloverStep.java#L57

Which only calls the listener with `complete == true` (and thus moves to the next step) if the index has rolled over

