When used in query_string - queries, the "cross_fields" match type overrides explicit fielded searches in the query string, resulting in unintended results. For instance:
`"query_string":{
  "query":"(foo AND bar) AND year:2018",
  "type":"cross_fields"
}`
will result in "2018" being searched in all fields as opposed to "year" only. The expected behaviour would be not to override explicitly specified fields...

